---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Jay Trainer — Music
description: "Jay Trainer is a singer-songwriter from Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. Explore folk, acoustic rock, and Americana music — eight releases spanning nearly two decades of storytelling and instinct."
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-distress" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">{{ site.location }}</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Jay<br><em>Trainer</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Songs born from deep-seated instinct. Stories forged in quiet rooms, beside fires, beneath old trees. Music that calls out and feels essential.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/music/" class="btn-primary">Hear the Music</a>
      <a href="/about/" class="btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HERO-TO-CONTENT TRANSITION -->
<div class="hero-crease" aria-hidden="true">
  <img src="/assets/images/paper-crease.png" alt="">
</div>

<!-- LISTEN / MUSIC -->
<section id="listen">
  <div class="section-label">Discography</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">The <em>Music</em></h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>

  {# Featured Release #}
  {% set featured = releases | findBySlug("a-whisper-of-ruin-deluxe") %}
  {% if featured %}
  <div class="featured-release reveal">
    <div class="featured-image-wrap">
      <a href="/music/{{ featured.slug }}/">
        <img src="{{ featured.coverArt }}" alt="{{ featured.title }}" loading="lazy">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="featured-content">
      <div class="featured-tag">Latest Album — {{ featured.year }}</div>
      <h3 class="featured-title">A Whisper Of <em>Ruin</em><br>— Deluxe Edition</h3>
      <p class="featured-desc">{{ featured.description }}</p>
      <div class="featured-tracklist">
        <ol>
          {% for track in featured.tracks %}
          <li><span>{{ track.title }}</span><span>{{ track.duration }}</span></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="featured-btns">
        <a href="/music/{{ featured.slug }}/" class="btn-primary">Stream & Download</a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- MUSIC GRID -->
  <div class="music-grid">
    {% for r in releases %}
      {% if not r.featured %}
        {% include "partials/music-card.njk" %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{% include "partials/streaming-banner.njk" %}

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-images">
      <img src="/assets/images/figure-misty-field.jpg" alt="Figure in misty field" class="about-img-main" loading="lazy">
      <img src="/assets/images/jay-recording.jpg" alt="Guitar close-up" class="about-img-secondary" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-label">The story</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">About <em>Jay</em></h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>For as long as I can remember I've been familiar with this deep-seated instinct within me. It told me the path my life would progress in and that regardless of where it takes me, I was obligated to this precondition.</p>
      <div class="about-quote">
        "Perhaps you've had a similar experience — something that called out to you profoundly and felt essential to your existence."
      </div>
      <p>Out of Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, Jay Trainer has spent years quietly building a body of work rooted in storytelling, acoustic honesty, and the kind of songs that feel like they've always existed — waiting to be discovered in the fog.</p>
      <p>From intimate recordings by firelight to wider studio sessions, each record is a chapter. The music doesn't chase trends. It grows like old trees — slowly, with deep roots, shaped by weather and time.</p>
      <a href="/about/" class="btn-primary btn-mt-sm">Read More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MERCH -->
<section id="merch">
  <div class="section-label">Shop</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Merch & <em>Physical</em></h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <p class="merch-intro">Take something home. Posters, apparel, and the full digital discography — all available through Bandcamp. Physical music for a world that moves too fast.</p>
  <div class="merch-grid">
    {% for item in merch %}
      {% include "partials/merch-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BLOG / JOURNAL -->
<section id="blog">
  <div class="section-label">Words</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">The <em>Journal</em></h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="blog-grid">
    {% for blogPost in collections.blog | reverse | limit(3) %}
      {% include "partials/blog-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
